<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>6816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天气很好的一天，一个农场的小女孩儿向集市走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17144</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的名字叫莫莉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莫莉在头顶上顶着一桶牛奶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她高兴地唱着歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真开心！集市上有许多好看的东西！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我卖了牛奶之后，买点儿什么东西好呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她思索着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯！让我想想！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是莫莉只有一桶牛奶，她卖不了很多钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我就买一只母鸡吧。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“买一只母鸡能干什么呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只母鸡能下很多很多的鸡蛋，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这些鸡蛋孵化了之后就可以有很多小鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有了这些小鸡我能干什么呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我喂这些小鸡以后，它们就会慢慢地长大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后它们会下更多的鸡蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鸡蛋孵化了之后，我会得到更多的小鸡！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太棒了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那样我可以卖更多的鸡蛋和小鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们都会过来买鸡或者鸡蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那样我就会变得很富有！”莫莉笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要买漂亮的衣服，金色的头饰，还有闪亮的鞋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会成为村子里最富有，最有名的人！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>总有一天，我会被邀请到皇宫里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都会嫉妒我！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会遇到帅气的王子，他会向我鞠躬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我也会向王子回礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会说‘王子殿下’，然后像这样鞠躬……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当莫莉鞠躬的时候，牛奶桶从她的头上掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛奶洒得到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莫莉大声哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>牛奶没有了，与牛奶一起消失的还有莫莉的美梦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>